  112: /* ============================================================
  113:  * HEADER TOOLBAR — single row, three semantic clusters
  114:  * (settings / icon utilities / CTAs), separated by subtle dividers.
  115:  * Inspired by the toolbars in Linear, Vercel dashboard and Stripe:
  116:  * 32-36px consistent tap targets, flat surfaces, one accent pop.
  117:  * ============================================================ */
  118: .header-ctrls{
  119:   position:relative;
  120:   display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;
  121:   justify-content:flex-end;
  122:   justify-self:end;
  123:   max-width:100%;
