  858:  * still toggles <details>: drag is triggered only after ~4px of movement
  859:  * (see makeOfflinePanelDraggable in JS). "grab" cursor signals the affordance. */
  860: body.mm-enlarged #offlineTilePanel > summary{
  861:   cursor:grab; user-select:none; touch-action:none;
  862:   padding:6px 0 10px;
  863:   border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  864:   margin-bottom:8px;
  865: }
  866: body.mm-enlarged #offlineTilePanel > summary::after{
