  903: /* ============== BBOX SELECTION ON MAP (draw-to-cache area) ==============
  904:  * User flow:
  905:  *   1) Click "Seleziona area sulla mappa" → .tile-map gets .bbox-selecting.
  906:  *      Cursor becomes crosshair, pan handlers yield to bbox handlers.
  907:  *   2) Mousedown + drag → a temporary .bbox-draft div is drawn in pixel
  908:  *      space. A floating .bbox-live-tip follows the cursor with a live
  909:  *      estimate (tiles / MB / area).
  910:  *   3) Mouseup → px corners are converted to lat/lon, stored in
  911:  *      state.bboxSelection, pcN/pcS/pcE/pcW are populated.
