 4713:     "help.guide.convert.title":"Convert a coordinate",
 4714:     "help.guide.convert.body":"Use the <b>Automatic input</b> field to paste any format (DD / DDM / DMS / UTM / MGRS / Plus Codes / Gauss-Boaga / ED50 / ROMA40). Press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>Enter</kbd> to convert. You instantly get all formats on WGS84, the permalink and the mini-map.",
