 4725:     "help.guide.tools.title":"Tools (Ctrl+K)",
 4726:     "help.guide.tools.body":"The <b>Tools</b> panel groups: <b>Batch</b> (bulk conversion), <b>Measure</b> (distance/bearing/area), <b>Range</b> (fire fan), <b>Astro</b> (sun/moon), <b>Magnetic</b> (WMM declination), <b>Track</b> (build polyline/polygon from points), <b>Favorites</b> and <b>Session</b>.",
 4727:     "help.guide.fav.title":"Favorites, history, notes",
 4728:     "help.guide.fav.body":"Save a point to <b>Favorites</b> with notes and tags, reopen from <b>History</b>, add annotations in the <b>Notes</b> panel. Everything stays local in your browser.",
