 7093: /**
 7094:  * Total geodetic length of a polyline / polygon.
 7095:  * Sums Vincenty-inverse distances between successive points.
 7096:  * @param {Array<{lat:number,lon:number}>} pts
 7097:  * @param {boolean} closed - if true, adds the segment from last back to first (perimeter mode).
 7098:  * @returns {number} length in meters
