 9915: /**
 9916:  * Top-level mini-map renderer: uses interactive OSM tiles when online (and
 9917:  * not force-offline), otherwise falls back to the schematic SVG map. Stores
 9918:  * the last point on `state` so the map can be re-rendered when the connection
 9919:  * state toggles.
