 9921: /**
 9922:  * Entry point for the mini-map. Chooses online (tiles) vs offline (SVG).
 9923:  * @param {number} lat point latitude
 9924:  * @param {number} lon point longitude
 9925:  * @param {boolean} resetView if true, recenters the map on the point (default
 9926:  *   for a brand-new conversion); if false, preserves the user's panned view
 9927:  *   (used by size/layer toggles which just re-render).
